        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "."
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "The laws are also a product of a national media ecosystem that still often bakes climate denial into its coverage. "
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "In that ecosystem, there is straight-up climate omission — climate-intensified weather disasters are often covered "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            19
          ],
          1,
          "without any mention"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " of their link to rising carbon in the atmosphere. "
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "But there is also often a lack of climate policy context that might provide voters with an idea of exactly who to hold accountable."
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "While there are certainly terrific outlets like the "
        ],
        [
          0,
